{"tid":745083,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺學科 weighting 都幾陰濕","createTime":"2018-07-16T12:30:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T05:28:13.000Z","uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"95a13c9d104733a3cf42d32215cdeabeff98bcbd","tid":745083,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T12:30:25.000Z","msg":"335(5)555，B5 25<br />\n<br />\nElectives 係 Chem Phy<br />\n<br />\nCity 同 HKU 好興將英文 x2<br />\n<br />\n就咁睇 55555 係 B5 25 分<br />\n但呢兩間學校會將英 x2，有啲 Electives x1<br />\n咁英文乘完 2 就會變 6 分，然後 B5 就會計英文而唔計乘 1 既 Electives，呢個 case 你 B5 就會因為佢乘大英文，逼走你一科 5 而減左好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n345(5)354，B5 23<br />\n呢個 case 英文 x2，x1 果科 Electives 低上面 1 分，但英文 x2，計完 weighting 反而高過上面 1 分<br />\n<br />\n最後 23 分入到但 25 分入唔到，好多人明明高過 LQ 都入唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc78ca334959aef851fafaf609a0b3c5bdcb8590","tid":745083,"uid":152520,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T12:34:01.000Z","msg":"系<br />\n有時同一科（有weighting) 直接睇best five 既話LQ仲高過median"},{"pid":"656368082d12d424317c1ed59dcf36ab1750808f","tid":745083,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T12:34:32.000Z","msg":"依個真"},{"pid":"f5e5da8158b5c0b7f8b626a19153b45d7f79fd91","tid":745083,"uid":171509,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T13:17:00.000Z","msg":"規則就寫左係度咁多年<br />\n你唔按章法出牌可以怪邊個"},{"pid":"629fe2c514f0fafd669e0240325eafa2f6d0779a","tid":745083,"uid":71543,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T13:26:04.000Z","msg":"陰濕得過poly啲weighting?<br />\n理科仔輕鬆入rd 視光"},{"pid":"21a858339b30a6cce6b944831d22a1f4386f521d","tid":745083,"uid":77473,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"629fe2c514f0fafd669e0240325eafa2f6d0779a","tid":745083,"uid":71543,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T13:26:04.000Z","msg":"陰濕得過poly啲weig